quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  28,29,"Mi ifukk Musa tallit, u iseyyeĂȘ akked twacult is, iwala times ar tama n udrar. Inna i twacult is: \"qqimet, wala$ times, ahat ad awen d awi$, segs, asali ne$ asafu, amar a ppesseĂȘmum"
  28,30,"Mi ibbwev $uĂŽes, ipwanced ed si ttejĂŽa, di rif ayeffus n te$zut, deg umviq iĂŽqan: \"a Musa! S tidep, Nek d Ăebbi, Mass imavalen"
  28,31,"VeggeĂŽ taĂąkwazt ik\". Mi p iwala, la tesseĂȘĂŽiĂźiw amzun d azrem, ibren ur iwexxeĂŽ. \"A Musa! Qeddem, ur ppagwad, aql ak, ih, di laman"
  28,32,"Err afus ik di loib ik, a d iffe$ d amellal, ur ihlik. SseqĂŽeb ed $uĂŽek i$il ik, ad ak tekkes tugwdi. Tigi d sin n ppbut s$uĂŽ Mass ik, i FerĂąun akked imvebbĂŽen is. Ih, nitni d agdud iballa$en"
  28,33,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Nek n$i$ yiwen segsen, ugade$ ad iyi n$en"
  28,34,"Gma Harun yif iyi afeĂ»Ă»eĂȘ umeslay. Azen it id yidi d amĂąiwen, ad iyi tebbet. Nek ugade$ ad iyi nekĂŽen"
  28,35,"Inna: \"a Nesseohed tayepp ik s gma k. Ad awen Nefk, i sin, adabu; ur kwen id ppawven. S issekniyen nneÂŁ, d kunwi akked wid iddan yidwen ara irebĂȘen"
  28,36,"Mi ibbwev $uĂŽsen Musa, s issekniyen iberrzen, nnan: \"ayagi, siwa ssĂȘur id innulfan. Ur nesli s waya, $uĂŽ ibabaten nne$ imezwura"
  28,37,"Inna Musa: \"Mass iw IĂ©ĂŽa sennig wiyav, anwa iwumi Ifka nnhaya s$uĂŽeS, anwa ara d igwrin deg Uxxam. Imednas, s tidep, ur rebĂȘen"
  28,38,"Inna FerĂąun: \"a yimvebbĂŽen, ur awen mli$ ara kra n ĂŽebbi, war nekkini. EcĂąal iyi times ar talaxt, a Haman; bnu yi lbeĂŽo aĂąlayen; ahat ad ali$ ar ĂĂebbi n Musa. Nek, s tidep, ĂȘesbe$ t seg wid iskiddiben"
  28,39,"Neppa, akked iĂąsekĂŽiwen is, sme$wĂŽen iman nnsen di tmurt, war ssebba. ÂŁilen, ar nitni, ur d ppu$alen $uĂŽneÂŁ"
  28,40,"Neppa, akked iĂąsekĂŽiwen is, NeĂźĂźef iten. Nger iten ar yill. Wali amek tevĂŽa d imednas"
  28,41,"Nerra ten d imeqwĂŽanen i ineccden ar tmes. Ass n tnekra, ur ppusellken"
  28,42,"Neqqen asen xezzu di ddunit agi. Ass n tnekra, nitni seg ucmiten"
  28,43,"Ni$ Nefka Tazmamt i Musa, mbaĂąd ma Nesqucc isuta imezwura. D tafat i imdanen, d nnhaya u d aĂȘunu. Amar a d mmektin"
  28,44,"Ur telliv ara di loiha utaram, mi Nseyya lameĂŽ i Musa. Ur telliv seg inagan"
  28,45,"Maca, Nxelq ed tisuta, $wezzif laĂąmeĂŽ nnsent. Ur tellid seg imezda$ n Madian, la sen teqqarev issekniyen nneÂŁ. Maca, Nella Neppazen"
  28,46,"Ur telliv ar tama n udrar, mi d Nessawel. Maca d aĂȘunu s$uĂŽ Mass ik, iwakken a pnedrev agdud, u$uĂŽ ur d iusi uneddaĂŽ, uqbel ik. Amar a d mmektin"
  28,47,"Mulac, ma tĂȘuza ten tiyta id urwen ifassen nnsen, a d inin: \"a Mass nne$! A lemmer i $ d Tuznev amazan, a neddu d issekniyen iK, a nili seg wid iumnen"
  28,48,"Mi ten id tusa tidep s$uĂŽneÂŁ, nnan: \"a lemmer id iusi am wayen id iusan i Musa\"! Day ur ugin ara, zik, ayen id iusan i Musa? Nnan: \"d sin ssĂȘurat\". Mwafaqen, nnan: \"nekwni nugi ten i sin"
  28,49,"Ini: \"awit ed Tazmamt, s$uĂŽ Ăebbi, i yifen snat agi, i nnhaya, ad ddu$ yides, ma tessawalem tidep"
  28,50,"Ma ur ak d rran ara, efhem ar ddan kan d lhawiyyat nnsen. Anwa innetlafen, sennig win iteddun d lhawiyya s, war nnhaya s$uĂŽ Ăebbi? Ăebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud imednas"